Voidface CoreML runtime — placeholder.

This directory holds the shipped CoreML artifact (`Voidface.mlpackage`)
and a small Swift Package that wraps it as
`Voidface.protect(_ image: CIImage) -> CIImage`.

The `.mlpackage` is generated by `src/voidface/export/coreml.py`. Do not
edit it by hand. See `../../Documentation/deployment/coreml.md`.
